  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Bahamas: Enhance Disaster Risk Reduction in Migrant Communities in New Providence, Abaco and Eleuthera</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Against the backdrop of COVID-19, recurrent hurricanes, and future disasters - especially cyclical events which are amplifying in intensity and frequency - the project contributes to the reduction of disaster risks in eight migrant communities in New Providence, Abaco and Eleuthera in the Bahamas through capacity building of local community-based organizations and non-governmental organizations, and implementation of community risk assessment and disaster risk reduction activities.</narrative>
  </description>
